Subject: [PATCH] Dashboard redesign: hero strip, pill stats, softened module
 cards
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Personalized Africa/Lagos greeting (morning / afternoon / evening)
- Photographic hero with green gradient overlay + CTA buttons
- Profile completion progress bar (shown while under 75%)
- Pill-chip stat strip: profile %, open opps, grants live (₦), members,
  price reports (7d) — all fetched in a single Promise.all
- Primary module grid (6 cards) with accent top-border on hover, filled
  icon tiles, optional badges, and meta footer
- Secondary row (Directory / Mentorship / Research) as compact tiles
- Keeps AppNav, OnboardingWizard gate, and FAQAccordion intact

Ships on branch only — production unaffected. Hero photo is Unsplash
(free license); flagged in IP strategy §5 for post-Beta replacement.
